@startuml cms_preview_sequence

title Диаграмма последовательности\nЗащищенный preview чернового контента

actor "Контент-менеджер" as Editor
participant "Strapi Admin UI" as AdminUi
participant "Preview config\napps/cms/config/admin.ts" as PreviewConfig
participant "Strapi documents service" as DocumentsService
participant "Frontend /api/preview" as PreviewApi
collections "Preview session\n__cms_preview cookie" as PreviewSession
participant "Frontend /preview/..." as PreviewPage
participant "Middleware\nenforce-published" as PublishGuard
participant "Strapi REST API" as CmsApi
database "SQLite" as SqliteDb

Editor -> AdminUi : Нажать Preview
AdminUi -> PreviewConfig : uid, documentId, locale, status

alt Preview for draft content
  PreviewConfig -> DocumentsService : findOne(documentId, locale)\nfields=[slug] for slug-based entities
  DocumentsService -> SqliteDb : Read current entry
  SqliteDb --> DocumentsService : Entry data
  DocumentsService --> PreviewConfig : slug or home target
  PreviewConfig --> AdminUi : /api/preview?secret=...&locale=...&type=...&slug=...&status=draft

  AdminUi -> PreviewApi : GET preview URL
  PreviewApi -> PreviewApi : Validate PREVIEW_SECRET,\nlocale and target type
  PreviewApi -> PreviewSession : Set httpOnly cookie
  PreviewApi --> PreviewPage : 307 Redirect /preview/...

  PreviewPage -> PreviewSession : Verify preview cookie
  PreviewPage -> PublishGuard : GET /api/...&status=draft\nx-preview-secret
  PublishGuard -> PublishGuard : Valid preview header,\nstatus is not forced
  PublishGuard -> CmsApi : Pass draft request
  CmsApi -> SqliteDb : Read draft entry
  SqliteDb --> CmsApi : Draft content
  CmsApi --> PreviewPage : Content + SEO data
  PreviewPage --> Editor : Render preview page\nwith noindex
else Entity already published
  PreviewConfig --> AdminUi : /api/preview?...&status=published
  AdminUi -> PreviewApi : GET preview URL
  PreviewApi -> PreviewSession : Clear preview cookie
  PreviewApi --> AdminUi : 307 Redirect to public URL
end

note over PublishGuard, CmsApi
Public GET /api/* requests without
x-preview-secret are forced to
status=published before the controller layer.
end note

@enduml
